		<body xml:space="preserve">
			<div type="dedication">
				<p xml:id="p1">stamp[at]o. [Tasso wrote four different versions of this poem, listed consecutively at 102r-102v in this source. The version transcribed below is the only one that Tasso did not erase.]</p>
			</div>
			<div>
				<lg>
					<l xml:id="l1">Come cristallo in monte,</l>
					<l xml:id="l2">l’orgoglio, in voi s’indura,</l>
					<l xml:id="l3">Donna bella, e crudele, ^superba^ oltra misura :</l>
					<l xml:id="l4">In me l’amore affina,</l>
					<l xml:id="l5">Come or lucente infiamma,</l>
					<l xml:id="l6">e se gela il cor vostro <del>agghiaccia</del>, ‘l mio s’infiamma :</l>
					<l xml:id="l7">Ne quella algente brina</l>
					<l xml:id="l8">struggi. p[er]ò: ma nel’istesso loco</l>
					<l xml:id="l9">Manterria fede eterna <del>il gi</del> al gelo il foco :</l>
				</lg>
			</div>
		</body>
